# Rules Catalog (Dewey-style)

## Classification System

Uses Dewey Decimal principles: hierarchical, numeric, extensible.

| Range | Category | Description |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| 000-099 | Foundations | Architecture, design philosophy, core principles |
| 100-199 | Tools | Linters, formatters, build tools |
| 200-299 | Languages | Language-specific conventions |
| 300-399 | Frameworks | Platform & framework rules |
| 400-499 | Testing | Testing standards & quality |
| 500-599 | Operations | CI/CD, monitoring, security |
| 600-699 | Documentation | Docs standards |
| 700-799 | Workflows | Git, PR, release processes |
| 800-899 | Project | Reserved for project-specific |
| 900-999 | Meta | Templates, indexes, deprecated |

